                    <h4 class="title">How Much is Fitrana 2025?</h4>
                    <p class="pera">
                        The amount of Fitrana is determined based on the value of staple foods like wheat, barley, dates, or raisins. For 2025, the estimated amount may vary depending on local food prices. Islamic scholars and organizations often announce the exact Fitrana amount closer to Ramadan’s end.
                        <br><br>
                        Typically, Fitrana is equivalent to the cost of approximately 2.5 kilograms of staple food per person. To ensure accuracy, you can consult your local mosque or Islamic organization. Donating the correct amount on time is crucial, as Fitrana must be distributed to the needy before the Eid prayer.


                    </p>
                

